Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.41,0:00:04.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一个硬币就能游戏通关的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.47,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,称呼我们为通关小子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:09.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,通关小子KID 是他的绰号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:13.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你就是KID
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:17.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一个硬币拿到太空战机的最高分 这是我的 目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:21.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个亮晶晶的女孩叫 什么名字来着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:24.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我叫高野文美 KID
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治才不是KID呢 我才是 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:30.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:33.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这么有趣的游戏怎么可能不玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.41,0:00:37.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,任天堂版啊 这种东西对于我们来说也没有什么意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我有了想在日本做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:43.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思我明白了  那就让我们用电脑游戏来决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:46.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,因为时间是有限的 做你喜欢的事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好的 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:51.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然是男的啊 小文美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:55.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我赢了的话 请和我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:58.07,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,安全地带 只能这样做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:00.07,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话我也抱着破釜沉舟的觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:02.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你已经无法自拔了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:04.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:06.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我就快要考试了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.18,0:01:08.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个游戏是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:12.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,毫不留情地袭击我们复习生意志的怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.29,0:01:15.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治和木户在另一个世界也要好好战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:22.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,赋闲一年后 终于
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:24.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,通过考试的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:29.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户的第一志愿 工学系的大学完全通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:33.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,踏出了迈向游戏设计师的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:37.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我总算是考上了保底的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:42.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,过上了所谓的普通的大学生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,然后 几年过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:59.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,很脆弱哪 啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:13.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:16.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 乐队的练习时间拖长了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:18.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治在搞乐队的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:22.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哦 摇滚的时代不是吗 话说 你发呆的看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:26.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个建筑物的窗户能看成俄罗斯方块的方块
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你的脑子里还真是只有游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢 礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:38.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,俄罗斯方块那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:41.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,革命性的理念以前有过吗——不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嘛 我也玩俄罗斯方块哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:48.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,俄罗斯方块很流行 和女孩儿搭讪时也是个好话题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:52.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那种不纯洁的动机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:56.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哈 那木户 大学生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:59.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是像俄罗斯方块那样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:02.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,经验就是各种方块堆积起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:06.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,特别是对于大学生活 最重要的方块是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:09.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:18.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话 礼治你有女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 虽然现在暂时是空窗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:27.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 好想和像田中美奈子这样的好女孩好好恋爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,读女性杂志什么的 有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:27.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不是 长知识了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:32.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,又登载了可爱女孩子的照片 嘛 真是大饱眼福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治的大学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的女孩子有很多不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不 像俄罗斯方块那种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:42.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,能非常契合地和我相嵌的并没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:46.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的型是苗条的 白白皮肤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:49.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,大眼睛 短头发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:53.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,又有点神秘感的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:57.27,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 嗯 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:06:00.27,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对 对 就是像这种的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:07.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是 是高野吧 诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,平面模特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:19.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好像 去了很远的地方的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,果然 礼治对高野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:50.27,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 不好了 要迟到了 要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 不好了 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:55.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,咚 啊咧 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:58.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 鞋带 开了 哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:03.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:56.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,果然 大学生活是像俄罗斯方块一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:59.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,总会出现那种一下就能契合相嵌的方块
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:01.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,的确是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:05.11,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,说话的时候相同的地方不断冒出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:09.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,听的音乐 喜欢的小说家  钟爱的电视剧 全都一样耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:12.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,入迷的游戏 尊敬的游戏编程者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:16.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,勇者斗恶龙三最终的队员构成也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:18.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你也
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:23.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嘛 这本书是他借我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,诶  快说快说 是什么样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:29.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很成熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:34.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得和他可以成为很好的伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:43.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你游戏玩过头 终于
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.07,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哈 没有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是如果和他的话应该可以做出很好的游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:50.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,游戏 不是关于女生的话题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:53.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治遇见的是 普通的关于女生的话好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:58.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,已经不再喜欢高野了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:03.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在刚开始就没喜欢好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:11.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,, 啊 对了  因为你说对这个有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:15.27,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我就做出来的  我最喜欢的曲目大全      谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:19.15,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,特别是第三首我最喜欢了 诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:22.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哦 朱里 裕介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,放在你家的东西不不去拿不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那件事下次再说吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:29.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:32.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个是谁 感觉好酷的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:35.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,前男友 裕介在我们还在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,被艺能事务所选拔出来过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,诶 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的有一拍即合的方块存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.11,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,喂 朱理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:48.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,前男友 裕介在我们还在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:52.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,被艺能事务所选拔出来过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:59.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,被艺能事务所选拔出来过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:05.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高中时带领大家打入全国篮球比赛的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:11.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,然后在大学得到正式会计师资格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:18.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有把在雨中被丢弃的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:24.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,带回家收养的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.15,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,完败啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:42.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,前男友什么的 你就那么在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.79,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会被比较啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:50.55,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个女孩儿也不是你的初恋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:54.43,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不 是初恋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:59.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,诶 但是你之前不是说只是暂时空窗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 现在和之前都没交过女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,非要我说得这么明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:15.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治  被称作名作的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:18.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,做第二季是非常难的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:21.03,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好啰嗦 何必让我更受打击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:24.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,比如太空战机2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:26.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,比起只有三个场景的第一季
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:29.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,的确冲击感变得淡了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:32.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,, 但是 最新采用的中boss
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,还有非常美丽的BGM
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:38.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,和非常出色的演出 让它成为了无法忘记的一部作品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:45.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得只要礼治有一点超过前男友的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:48.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,她就是认同你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:12.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那些事 别提了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:20.27,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,瞳真的厉害过头了 哪里厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,裕介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:32.55,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我要是没法越过你这道阻碍 就没法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,俄罗斯彩球  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:56.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,用这个来决胜负吧 啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是俄罗斯方块啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,还是学生的你们不会明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,有各种各样的事啊 大人们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:14.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 说道大人的状况 明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:17.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:19.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,俄罗斯彩球是把从上面掉下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:21.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,同样颜色的宝石横纵斜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,三个以上放到一起就可以消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:27.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,连续把宝石消除叫做连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:30.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一直这样继续下去的话就能得到最高分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:33.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个规则真的是划时代的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:36.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,甚至说以后这种游戏会成为标准
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,也不会过头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:42.15,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊 话说你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:44.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我叫木戸明信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:49.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,取得最高分的人得到朱理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:52.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吧 朱理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:56.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 嘛 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:01.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那 游戏开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:21.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不愧是让朱理迷恋过的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:24.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哎 没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:50.47,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,分数是22万6649分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:53.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对12万9666
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:58.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,胜利的人是礼治君 哦 耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:18:01.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户 我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:09.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这儿样好吗 这么大的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:12.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,却用游戏决定了 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:15.31,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也没想跟朱理复合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:24.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 朱理 礼治君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:28.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我有话想告诉你 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:31.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:34.32,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哦 朱理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:37.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,阿健
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:42.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友？ 呃 在裕介之前的男友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:49.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,朱理 你好吗 隆弘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:54.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这个是朋友吧 前前前男友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,朱理 很久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:01.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 阿友 直树
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:09.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是前前前前男友 旁边是再之前的男友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:16.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,前男友到底有几个啊 数不清了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:22.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,可是 大学生活就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要这样做来积累经验的生活吧 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 阿弘 哦 朱理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:34.43,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对了 想说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:39.43,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:03.31,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户 我错了啊 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:06.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我还是喜欢高野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:10.15,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 高野刚才经过这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:12.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:35.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我有话对你说 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:39.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,文美 文美 久等了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:43.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦 诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:48.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,朋友吗 啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:50.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你要说什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:57.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:20.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,MARS公司的相机在IT行业中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:23.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,被怀疑接受了不正当巨额资金
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:25.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正在MARS公司楼下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:27.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,担任MARS公司共同代表的木户氏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:31.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,尚未现身 根据公司内部消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:35.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:38.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:42.79,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,话说在前头 这是你欠的钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:46.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,还钱的钱有了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,有啊  净胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:52.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不支付赔偿金的话 连离婚都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:56.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人哪儿来什么钱还债
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你想过我的生活会怎样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:02.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,看看现实吧 现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:15.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这种狗屁现实我才懒得看呢
